&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;8c04i0&quot; data-start=&quot;120&quot; data-end=&quot;285&quot;&gt;Own operating expense (OPEX) forecasting and budget maintenance by ensuring routine and non-routine transactions are accurately reflected across departmental P&amp;amp;Ls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;el7q66&quot; data-start=&quot;286&quot; data-end=&quot;400&quot;&gt;Partner with department leaders to evaluate, challenge, and document the assumptions that drive operating costs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;12zqygo&quot; data-start=&quot;401&quot; data-end=&quot;530&quot;&gt;Build reports, presentations, and financial analyses that provide actionable insights for leadership and external stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1n1dh94&quot; data-start=&quot;531&quot; data-end=&quot;624&quot;&gt;Play a key role in migrating driver-based financial models from spreadsheets to Drivetrain.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1fwj6iz&quot; data-start=&quot;625&quot; data-end=&quot;788&quot;&gt;Support the Manager, FP&amp;amp;A on strategic initiatives and ad hoc projects, including fundraising, M&amp;amp;A, and the evolution of balance sheet and cash flow forecasting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;jg08dc&quot; data-start=&quot;789&quot; data-end=&quot;923&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;Leverage AI tools like Claude to streamline workflows, enhance analysis, draft first-pass commentary, and validate financial models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
